---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Dove operiamo — Tecno Consult Srl"
  description="Tecno Consult opera in Veneto e Friuli Venezia Giulia: 9 marchi rappresentati, grossisti, installatori, tecnici e progettisti."
>

<div class="wrap banner-image-wrap reveal">
  <img class="banner-image" src="/images/stock-cantiere.jpg" alt="Mezzo da cantiere sul territorio" loading="lazy" />
</div>

<section>
  <div class="wrap dove">
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px;">Dove operiamo</p>
      <p style="line-height:1.7;">Operiamo nel mercato idro-termo-sanitario, condizionamento, trattamento aria e acqua ed energie alternative — settori civile, industriale, terziario, commerciale, navale, alberghiero e termale.</p>
      <ul class="dove-list">
        <li><b>Veneto</b> (tutte le province per almeno un marchio)</li>
        <li><b>Friuli Venezia Giulia</b> (copertura completa)</li>
        <li><b>Trentino</b> (Radiant e ITAP)</li>
        <li><b>Grossisti</b>, rivenditori, installatori, tecnici e progettisti</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="maps-embed">
        <iframe
          src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Via+Barcis+2,+30027+San+Don%C3%A0+di+Piave+VE+Italy&t=&z=13&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"
          width="100%"
          height="320"
          style="border:0; border-radius:var(--radius); filter:grayscale(20%);"
          allowfullscreen
          loading="lazy"
          referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
          title="Sede Tecno Consult — San Donà di Piave">
        </iframe>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<svg class="pipe-divider" viewBox="0 0 1180 34" preserveAspectRatio="none"><path d="M0,17 H500 V29 H680 V17 H1180" stroke="#2d5563" stroke-width="1.6" fill="none" opacity="0.5"/></svg>

<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <p class="eyebrow">Marchi rappresentati</p>
      <p>Territorio di competenza per ciascun marchio.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="brand-territory-grid reveal">
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/aquatechnik.png" alt="Aquatechnik" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Aquatechnik Group SpA</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto (tranne VR) · FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/radiant.svg" alt="Radiant" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Radiant Bruciatori SpA</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto (tranne RO) · FVG · Trento</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/gda.jpg" alt="GDA" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">General D'Aspirazione</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto (tranne VR e RO) · FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/itap.jpg" alt="ITAP" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Itap SpA</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto · FVG · Trento</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/gia.png" alt="GIA" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">GIA SpA</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/fantini-cosmi.png" alt="Fantini Cosmi" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Fantini Cosmi SpA</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto (tranne VR) · FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/winkler-solar.png" alt="Winkler Solar" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Winkler Solar</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">VI · PD · RO · FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/swell-system.png" alt="Swell System" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">Swell System</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto (tranne VR) · FVG (tranne TS)</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bt-card">
        <div class="bt-logo"><img src="/images/brands/oli.jpg" alt="OLI" /></div>
        <div class="bt-info">
          <div class="bt-name">OLI Srl</div>
          <div class="bt-zone">Veneto · FVG</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
